data.description: Welcome home to the community of Silverstone Ranch! This two story, two car garage home has 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms and when you walk into the home it has a two story great room and a beautiful staircase. The kitchen has a ton of cabinets and you can walk right out to the covered patio for the perfect BBQ area! NEW CARPET FRESH PAINT
